# Source0-md5:	065ba41828644eca5dd8163446de5d64
Patch0:		%{name}-uname-cpuinfo.patch
Patch1:		%{name}-mem.patch
URL:		http://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/
BuildRequires:	acl-devel
